show_dbs = 󰲟dev𝘋𝘉􀊱tok𝘋𝘉ᐵ.show􀃅

𝐇    = 􀌖‹⬤;⬤›  encode device identifier from 𝐭 and 𝐮
is𝐇  = 󷺹􀋙⁰ᔨ␛;􁀨0􀝕⟞􀊹􈇊
